{"tid":123963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我從來沒有遇見你","createTime":"2017-02-17T08:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T09:45:25.000Z","uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da7c2d3298a2c660b91b2ed935e93bbd0cf391b3","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今年即將踏入2字頭 <br />\n<br />\n曾經係中學時期拍過一次拖<br />\n<br />\n自從嗰次之後一直無對過任何女仔有興趣<br />\n<br />\n一直都對愛情無咩感覺 <br />\n<br />\n直至小弟今年出國讀書遇到左一個女仔<br />\n<br />\n第一眼開始已經對佢有好感 <br />\n<br />\n但係佢好似對我愛理不理咁<br />\n<br />\n有段時間好想停一停唔揾佢 <br />\n<br />\n點之過左段時間更加掛住佢<br />\n<br />\n覺得佢真係好特別 好想可以同佢進一步發展<br />\n<br />\n但同時理智的我想 move on<br />\n<br />\n呢段時間我對所有野都好冷感 夜晚合埋眼就諗起佢<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以插醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c60786e6fdef30ef50ebe3193d3582371423b45","tid":123963,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"其實你冇你想像中咁多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3250419855d2b016815d32a3f7bda516918c62b","tid":123963,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:34:20.000Z","msg":"Long d冇一齊可能係個更加好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce860bc2903d7b410820dfaa913eac0e4e8d03f","tid":123963,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Long d冇一齊可能係個更加好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 眼殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b68814787232b3e4378d5a9f49c9183bc2a553","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你冇你想像中咁多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好想揾返可以感受到正常感覺嘅自己 我對所有嘢都好似無曬興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d7905b3e2d9ec2e9d486b7305688f966fcda17","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Long d冇一齊可能係個更加好嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係long d係外國識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29ead1e26d80f9b1cf475ae9c8fc6439653d95e","tid":123963,"uid":47941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"I'm suffering the same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4fde0b5c1ef5dc43d6c4c2e34364d08a8b7076","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I'm suffering the same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實個感覺真係好無奈 覺得自己終於搵到個有興趣同佢發展既人但佢心中有無你都唔知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4237d7241e2c8dacbc4a51fc4b68378aa2bd7c","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I'm suffering the same <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天總是愛戲弄人<br />\n<br />\n給你遇見，沒說給你機會"},{"pid":"a7e787541569ffe43d41383bcb4eaa9ae5a65c8c","tid":123963,"uid":83856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0d3c426280db1636bb7421890f5803016a